Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Beat cream cheese and seasoning with electric mixer on medium speed until well blended. Spread onto bottom of 9-inch pie plate; top with 1 cup of the mozzarella cheese, the pizza sauce and remaining mozzarella cheese. Bake 15 to 20 min. or until dip is heated through and cheese is melted. Serve with the crackers.